They=E2=80=99re going to try and destroy him in cross-examination, because =
Harry=E2=80=99s case is pretty straightforward. Harry says, =E2=80=9CThere =
may have been people in the
palace who knew about this unlawful intrusion, but I didn=E2=80=99t know, a=
nd therefore I wasn=E2=80=99t able to exercise my rights.=E2=80=9D The news=
paper, on the other hand, says, =E2=80=9CWell, of course you knew, and you =
